Taft was first listed as a [[census-designated place]] in the [[2000 United States census]].<ref name=2000CensusLA>{{Cite web |title=2000 Census of Population - Population and Housing Unit Counts - Louisiana |publisher=United States Census Bureau |date=2000 |url=https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/2003/dec/phc-3-20.pdf |access-date=May 1, 2026}}</ref> The CDP first appeared with a population of zero in 2000. Its population was 63 in 2010 and 61 in 2020.<ref name=2010CensusP2 /><ref name=2020CensusP2 />

